        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewelry trends come and go, but earrings remain timeless. From adding grace to your workwear to being the centerpiece of your evening look, earrings define how you express your style. Yet, with so many varieties - danglers, drops, huggies, hoops, balis and J-balis it’s easy to wonder what truly sets each apart.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, each design is more than just an accessory - it’s an emotion captured in precious metal and ethically crafted stones. Whether you’re shopping online at Lucira’s official site or visiting a Lucira experience store in <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur</span></a>, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sky-city-borivali-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Mumbai</span></a>, or their newer location on <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/pune-store\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">JM Road in Pune</span></a>, understanding earring styles will help you make choices that enhance your natural elegance and suit every occasion.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_q6jXJi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. Danglers vs. Drops: Movement, Elegance and Statement",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1. Danglers vs. Drops: Movement, Elegance and Statement</h2><p>Danglers and drops are often confused, but the difference lies in their movement and length.</p>",
            "custom_id": "danglers",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_iTBp7C": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Danglers_vs._Drops_Movement_Elegance_and_Statement.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Drops hang just below the earlobe and typically stay still. They’re designed with simplicity in mind think of a single pearl, gemstone, or diamond drop that adds effortless sophistication. They work perfectly for office wear, formal gatherings, and brunches.</li><li>Danglers, however, are designed for movement. They sway gracefully as you walk, creating a fluid shimmer that draws attention. Long danglers with delicate chains or layers are ideal for evening events or festive occasions.</li></ul><p>If you’re pairing earrings with necklaces, explore Lucira’s exquisite<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">collections</span></a> for pieces that blend seamlessly with your preferred earring type - be it minimalist drops or ornate danglers.</p><p>Styling Tip: For round or oval faces, opt for long danglers to elongate your look. For angular or narrow faces, shorter drops add balance and charm.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_edc69T": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2. Huggies vs. Hoops: Comfort Meets Confidence",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>2. Huggies vs. Hoops: Comfort Meets Confidence</h2><p>When it comes to versatile elegance, huggies and hoops are timeless favorites. They both share a circular design but differ in fit, size, and overall feel.</p>",
            "custom_id": "huggies",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_bfhiR9": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Huggies_vs._Hoops_Comfort_Meets_Confidence.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Huggies are small earrings that “hug” your earlobes snugly. Their minimal design makes them ideal for daily wear and layering with multiple piercings. Pair them with a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond necklace</span></a> to complete an understated, luxurious look that transitions easily from work to dinner.</li><li>Hoops, by contrast, are larger circles that can range from thin metallic bands to diamond-studded statements. They symbolize boldness and are perfect for those who love making a confident style statement.</li></ul><p>Styling Tip: Medium-sized hoops add structure to round faces, while larger hoops enhance sharper jawlines. Try pairing your hoops with a sleek bun or ponytail for an effortlessly chic vibe.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. Balis vs. J-Balis: The Perfect Blend of Culture and Modernity",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>3. Balis vs. J-Balis: The Perfect Blend of Culture and Modernity</h2>",
            "custom_id": "balis",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_mBezGM": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Balis_vs._J-Balis_The_Perfect_Blend_of_Culture_and_Modernity.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Balis have deep roots in Indian tradition. Their full-circle design symbolizes eternity and unity, making them a beloved choice across generations. They’re perfect for traditional outfits and festive occasions where you want to exude grace.</li><li>J-Balis, on the other hand, are a modern adaptation of this classic. Instead of a full loop, they feature a distinctive “J” curve that gives them a trendy twist while maintaining a hint of cultural nostalgia.</li></ul><p>For those who appreciate subtle glamour, pair your balis or J-balis with a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a>. The rose-gold hue complements both modern and ethnic attire beautifully.</p><p>Styling Tip: J-Balis look stunning with Indo-Western outfits, while traditional balis bring an authentic charm to sarees, lehengas, and kurtas.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Choosing the Perfect Earrings for Your Face Shape",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>4. Choosing the Perfect Earrings for Your Face Shape</h2><p>Earrings can do more than accessorize - they can frame your face beautifully. Here’s how to choose:</p>",
            "custom_id": "choosing",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_e4NhYk": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Choosing_the_Perfect_Earrings_for_Your_Face_Shape.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PMD43g": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Round face: Long danglers or angular J-balis create the illusion of length.</li><li>Oval face: You’re luck -almost all earring types suit you, from drops to hoops.</li><li>Square face: Soften strong jawlines with curved balis or hoops.</li><li>Heart-shaped face: Try huggies or short danglers that balance the face shape.</li></ul><p>Lucira’s craftsmanship ensures that no matter your style, you’ll find earrings that feel as good as they look.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ngikYe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Material and Craftsmanship: Why It Matters",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>5. Material and Craftsmanship: Why It Matters</h2>",
            "custom_id": "material",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_A6TdbJ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Style_Earrings_for_Different_Occasions.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Rpx7eQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The beauty of an earring lies in its detailing - the metal finish, diamond cut, and overall balance. Lucira’s earrings, crafted in gold, rose gold, and silver tones, feature precision-cut lab-grown diamonds that offer the same brilliance as mined ones - minus the environmental impact.</p><p>For those curious about ethical luxury, explore transparent options like the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a>, which reflect Lucira’s commitment to sustainable elegance</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YYJNi4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. How to Style Earrings for Different Occasions",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>6. How to Style Earrings for Different Occasions</h2>",
            "custom_id": "how-to",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_bx8xra": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Style_Earrings_for_Different_Occasions_27d6129f-def1-4e61-b289-623d5374d1f8.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7XUeeT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Workwear: Choose delicate drops or huggies for subtle sophistication.</li><li>Casual Outings: Medium hoops or small balis keep the vibe chic yet comfortable.</li><li>Festive Occasions: Statement danglers or J-balis add traditional charm.</li><li>Evening Events: Go bold with diamond-studded hoops or long metallic danglers.</li></ul><p>Pairing your earrings with complementary necklaces or bracelets adds an extra layer of polish - because every detail matters.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Thoughts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Thoughts</h2><p>From subtle drops to bold hoops, and from classic balis to modern J-balis, each earring style tells a different story. The beauty lies in choosing what feels uniquely <em>you</em>. At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira</span></a>, every piece is crafted with precision, care, and a touch of conscious luxury - helping you shine effortlessly through every occasion.</p>",
            "custom_id": "final",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
